Goals
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Enumerate
Communicate effectively, and explain mathematics both verbally and in writing.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Demonstrate the ability to use and understand multiple representations (includin
g graphical, numerical and analytical) of mathematical concepts.
\end_layout

