Determine which computational tool is the most appropriate to use for a
 given task.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Create histograms and boxplots, and calculate basic statistical measures
 using a spreadsheet.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Complete basic algebraic manipulations using a computer algebra system.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Write about mathematics using a mathematical typesetting engine.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Understand the difference between raster and vector graphics, and when and
 how to use each.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Create geometric constructions electronically.
\end_layout

